\v 1 Mina ngasengiphenduka\x + 3.16. 4.7.\x* ngabona incindezelo zonke ezenziwa ngaphansi kwelanga\x + 5.8. 7.7.\x*; khangela-ke inyembezi zabacindezelweyo, njalo babengelamduduzi\x + Lilo 1.2.\x*; lehlangothini lwababacindezelayo kwakulamandla, kodwa babengelamduduzi\x + Lilo 1.2.\x*.
\v 2 Ngakho ngancoma abafileyo\x + Jobe 3.11-22.\x*, abavele sebefile, okwedlula abaphilayo\x + 1.10.\x*, abalokhu besaphila\x + 4.3.\x*.
\v 3 Yebo ungcono kulabo bobabili, ongakabi khona\x + Jobe 3.11-22.\x*\x + 5.3.\x*, ongabonanga umsebenzi omubi owenziwa ngaphansi kwelanga\x + 4.3.\x*.
\p
\v 4 Ngasengibona mina wonke umtshikatshika lempumelelo yonke yomsebenzi, ngoba lokhu kungumhawu womuntu ovela kumakhelwane wakhe\x + Zaga 13.8.\x*. Lokhu lakho kuyize lokukhathazeka komoya\x + 1.14.\x*.
\v 5 Isiphukuphuku sigoqa izandla zaso\x + Zaga 6.10. 24.33.\x* sidle inyama yaso\x + Isa. 9.20.\x*.
\v 6 Singcono isandla\x + Zaga 15.16.\x* esigcwele ukuthula\x + 6.5. 9.17. Zaga 29.9.\x* kulezandla ezimbili ezigcwele ukutshikatshika lokukhathazeka komoya\x + 1.14.\x*.
\p
\v 7 Mina ngasengiphenduka ngabona ize ngaphansi kwelanga\x + 4.1. 9.11.\x*.
\v 8 Kukhona oyedwa, njalo kakho owesibili, yebo kalamntwana kumbe umfowabo, njalo kakulakuphela komtshikatshika wakhe wonke, lelihlo lakhe kalisuthiswa yinotho\x + Zaga 27.20. 1 Joha. 2.16.\x*, njalo \add katsho ukuthi\x + Eks. 18.4.\x*\add*: Ngitshikatshikela bani, ngenze umphefumulo wami uswele okuhle\x + Hlab. 39.6.\x*? Lokhu lakho kuyize, yebo, kungumsebenzi omubi\x + 1.13.\x*.
\v 9 Ababili bangcono kuloyedwa, ngoba balomvuzo omuhle ngokutshikatshika kwabo.
\v 10 Ngoba uba besiwa omunye uzamvusa umngane wakhe; kodwa maye kuye oyedwa nxa esiwa, ngoba kungekho owesibili ongamvusa\x + 10.16.\x*.
\v 11 Futhi uba ababili belala ndawonye, ngakho balokukhudumala; kodwa ngoyedwa angakhudumala njani\x + 1 Kho. 1.1.\x*?
\v 12 Njalo uba omunye engehlula oyedwa, ababili bazamelana laye\x + 6.10. Jobe 14.20.\x*; lentambo elemicu emithathu kayiqanyulwa masinyane\x + Zaga 22.20.\x*.
\p
\v 13 Umfana ongumyanga ohlakaniphileyo\x + 9.15,16. Dute. 8.9.\x* ungcono\x + 1 Kho. 11.26. 12.2.\x* kulenkosi endala eyisithutha\x + Zaga 30.2.\x* engasakwazi ukwelulekwa\x + 12.12. Hlab. 19.11.\x*.
\v 14 Ngoba\x + Gen. 41.14.\x* uyaphuma entolongweni ukuthi abe yinkosi\x + Hlu. 16.21,25.\x*, lanxa futhi owayezelwe embusweni wakhe esiba ngumyanga\x + 1 Kho. 11.11,12. 12.19.\x*.
\v 15 Ngabona bonke abaphilayo abahamba ngaphansi kwelanga, lomfana wesibili ozakuma esikhundleni sakhe\x + 1 Kho. 12.20.\x*.
\v 16 Kakulasiphetho sabantu bonke, sabo bonke ababephambi kwabo, lalabo abeza emva kabayikuthokoza ngaye\x + 1 Kho. 13.33,34.\x*. Isibili lokhu lakho kuyize lokukhathazeka komoya\x + 1.14.\x*.